Validate
Validate pom.xml
Compile
Compile java classes
Test
Run Junit test cases
Package
Create artifact( jar, war, ear)
Verify
Can be integrated with integration test frameworks
Install
Copies artifacts to local repository
Deploy
Uploads artifacts to remote repository

